Oariem is around 300 in fletching, and made hinges/brackets when he needed metalworking and I tailored to get my cloth skill up which also increased my leather working...all his secondary skills are in the 275+ level now (tailoring is still very low though).<br>
<br>
I heard about a trick that helps on your consignments.  DON'T work up your metal working!  If you don't work up your metalworking, you will ONLY be given consignments to make bows, since the highest levels require you to have metalworking high.  And since you are only given consignments that you can actually complete, it should always be the highest level bow you can make.  You will not be given arrow consignments...so before you try increasing your metalworking, you may try getting a few consignments (your cloth still have to be pretty high though).<br>
